Class LinkedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinkedList
  • public class LinkedList
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Annice Najafi Description: Our linkedList class allowed insertions and deletions at only the front and the back of the linked list. These capabilities were convenient for us when we used inheritance or composition to produce a stack class and a queue class with minimal code simply by reusing the list class. Linked lists are normally more general than those we provided. Modify the linked-listclass we developed in this chapter to handle insertions and deletions anywhere in the list.
